2006-10-27  claw

	* src/cutil/AbstractInputStream.h, AbstractOutputStream.h, Makefile.am:

	  added abstract representation of an input and output stream.

	* src/cutil/InputReader.h, BufferedOutputWriter.h
	  src/InputReader.cc, BufferedOutputWriter.cc:

	  add convenience wrappers around AbstractInputStream and AbstractOutputStream
	  to simplify writing of data to a stream.

	* src/cutil/NamedPipe.h, Socket.h
	  src/NamedPipe.cc, Socket.cc, Makefile.am:

	  now implement both AbstractInputStream and AbstractOutputStream.

	  moved most reading and writing methods to InputReader and BufferedOutputWriter.

	* src/ServerSocket.cc

	  fixed typo in comment in passing.

